text: Frederick John Austin Barker (31 October 1903 – 6 May 1974) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Collingwood and Hawthorn in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Fred Barker's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1903 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players Category:Hawthorn Football Club players Category:Sportspeople from Melbourne
